</ship>

<event name="RKS_STORE_SNIPER_WIN">
	<text>Sniper Girl wastes no time hailing you. "They just keep coming, with better equipment every time, to rob us. I just can't catch a breath. I know that's why you're here too..." You're about to say something to cheer her up when she cuts you off. "Because there's NO better shop in this universe for Stealth gear! So efficient, pirates dream about it, coalitions plot to acquire it, and renegades jump in to steal it! Buy while you still can!".
		Turns out she's still in character. RK sector professionals must have seen some shit, you think to yourself.

		"...And for your timely assistance, here's a little incentive to buy." You realize the gift is your "Thank you", and shrug.
		Then you take one look at the wares and immediately understand why the attacker came here.

		"Oh and, some of this stuff is so hard to source it shouldn't even exist, so only 1 purchase per customer. But for you I'll make it 3."
	</text>
	<autoReward level="HIGH">standard_no_item</autoReward>

	<store>STORE_RKS_SNIPER</store>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Alright then.</text>
		<event/>
	</choice>
</event>

